                            </li>
                            <li class="sub-menu-items">
                                <a href="#footer" class="contact-us">Contact Us</a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="menu-items">
                        <a href="/my-profile" class="account">My Profile</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="landing-info" id="landing-info">
            <h3>Welcome to <span>CSS .  </span> We are dedicated to ensure that cancer patients in Kenya get access to quality and specialized medication from the best oncologists in the country.</h3>
            <a href="/appointments/view-all-appointments" class="appointment-btn">View All Appointments</a>
        </div>

    </div>


     <!-----------------About Us Page------------------>

    <div class="about-body" id="about-body">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="about-wrap">
            <div class="about-img">
                <img src="/icons/pexels-ivan-samkov-4989167.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h4>The Cancer Support System is a system that boasts itself in connecting cancer patients to the best oncologists in the country. <br><br>The system enables our patients to make online bookings for physical appointments and also to have online consultations with their preferred oncologists.  <br><br>The oncologists have been verified to ensure quality treatment for our patients.  <br><br>Our patients are advised to make relationships with oncologists through physical appointments before having online consultations <br><br>Please send your feedback or inquiries through our email provided at the bottom of this page.</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


   
